This is a project using AstroJS and the astro integration toolkit.

This project is a prometheus middleware integration for astro.

This project is divided in 3 sections:

- `/packages/`: Here is the code for the astro integrations.
- `/playgrounds/`: Here are the astro playgrounds for the different integrations
- `/`: root of the project, using changesets to release changes.

This Project also uses biome for linting, pnpm as a package manager and changesets.